        "timestamp": "2017-11-13 16:05:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAgree the section is needed, need input from vnfrqts PTL... Should this be a new section under users -or- should we rename \"VNF Provider Guidelines and Requirements\" to \"VNF Provider\" and show multiple sections within this eg Guidelines, Requirements, On-Boarding, Distributing?  Adding reviewers",
